[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       5[0m:[38;5;10m[49m > This recipe uses Amazon Comprehend Medical for entity/event detection, Amazon Comprehend (Custom Classification) for temporal relation classification, and DynamoDB for timeline storage. The hybrid approach (rule-based temporal expression recognition + ML-based relation classification + constraint propagation) is the pattern you'll see in production systems.
