[0m[1G[0m[0m[?25h{"verdict": "pass", "rationale": "The implementation demonstrates the recipe pattern end-to-end with 7 clearly labeled steps: preprocessing, entity detection via Comprehend Medical (detect_entities_v2), temporal expression recognition, candidate pair generation, relation classification via Comprehend Custom Classification (classify_document), temporal graph construction with transitivity propagation and cycle resolution, timeline generation, and DynamoDB storage. All boto3 API calls use correct method names (detect_entities_v2, classify_document, put_item) with proper parameters. Error handling is addressed through confidence thresholds, retry configuration (adaptive mode with max_attempts=3), cycle resolution logic, and detailed logging. The code includes synthetic healthcare data (a discharge summary with realistic temporal expressions), full algorithm implementations (topological sort, DFS cycle detection, regex temporal parsing), and interpretation of results. There are no placeholder/stub implementations—every function contains complete working logic. The 'Gap Between This and Production' section provides honest commentary without leaving stubs in the code itself."}